{"entryId":"87036eba-4134-4915-93e2-ee5062977f5a","conversationHistoryId":"oddchat_topic-topic-20260409t104357-26167605","entryKind":"message","actorRef":{"id":"participant:claude:ec50344f-8a27-45ed-96dc-52f74388432d","label":"Claude · shell-1","source":"agent","relatedSessionId":"ec50344f-8a27-45ed-96dc-52f74388432d"},"createdAt":"2026-04-09T03:39:01.063Z","payload":{"roomId":"topic:topic_20260409T104357_26167605","senderId":"participant:claude:ec50344f-8a27-45ed-96dc-52f74388432d","senderLabel":"Claude · shell-1","title":"This is the odd_manager project — a GTL (Graph Traversal Language) workspace manager. It has:","content":"This is the odd_manager project — a GTL (Graph Traversal Language) workspace manager. It has:\n\n- **GTL runtime** (.genesis/): Graph-first language with ABG interpreter, event-sourced traversal, recursive selection, and materialization.\n- **React+Vite frontend** (build_tenants/react_vite/): Dashboard with OddBoard (topic/graph visualization), OddTerm (terminal pool), OddChat (this room), and RuntimePanel components.\n- **Node server**: Manages terminal sessions, OddChat participant coordination, IRC gateway, and the oddboard topic/room system.\n- **Specification**: Requirements covering live coordination, session workspaces, provider adapters, and durable records.\n\nThe topic we are on — code_surface — sits on the Bootstrap Asset Graph in the graphs view. The project is actively being developed with recent work on terminal color handling, GTL sync, and graph function registry.","path":null,"source":"agent","messageKind":"chat","relatedSessionId":"ec50344f-8a27-45ed-96dc-52f74388432d","selectedTrainId":null,"stationId":null,"edgeId":null}}
