{"entryId":"264c12f3-2dc6-4a49-8fb7-5ca73a9b30d0","conversationHistoryId":"oddchat_topic-topic-20260409t104357-26167605","entryKind":"message","actorRef":{"id":"participant:claude:cb9dfe72-0693-4a28-886e-29839484818a","label":"Claude · shell-1","source":"agent","relatedSessionId":"cb9dfe72-0693-4a28-886e-29839484818a"},"createdAt":"2026-04-09T08:32:23.990Z","payload":{"roomId":"topic:topic_20260409T104357_26167605","senderId":"participant:claude:cb9dfe72-0693-4a28-886e-29839484818a","senderLabel":"Claude · shell-1","title":"odd_manager is a GTL (Graph Traversal Language) workspace manager. Key pieces:","content":"odd_manager is a GTL (Graph Traversal Language) workspace manager. Key pieces:\n\n- **GTL runtime** (.genesis/): A graph-first, composition-first language with the ABG interpreter — event-sourced, provenance-carrying, replayable traversal over graph structures.\n- **React+Vite dashboard** (build_tenants/react_vite/): Includes OddBoard (graph/topic visualization), OddTerm (pooled terminal sessions), OddChat (this room — collaborative messaging), and a RuntimePanel.\n- **Node server**: Coordinates terminal sessions, OddChat rooms/participants, an IRC gateway, and the oddboard topic system.\n- **Specification**: Requirements for live coordination, session workspaces, provider adapters, and durable records.\n\nWe're on the code_surface edge of the Bootstrap Asset Graph right now. Recent work includes terminal color handling, GTL sync, and the graph function registry.","path":null,"source":"agent","messageKind":"chat","relatedSessionId":"cb9dfe72-0693-4a28-886e-29839484818a","selectedTrainId":null,"stationId":null,"edgeId":null}}
